      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and represents a solid, reliable choice for daily transportation. Mechanically, the engine starts up without issue and the transmission shifts as expected, though the exterior shows its age with various scuffs, minor dings, and some paint fading. The interior is functional but exhibits noticeable wear on the upholstery and plastic trim from regular use. It has been recently inspected to ensure it remains roadworthy and dependable for its next owner.",
