    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled preservation. This vehicle remains in an exemplary state, having undergone an exhaustive multi-point certification process to ensure mechanical and aesthetic perfection. The interior remains in showroom condition, free of any discernible wear, while the exterior maintains its original factory luster. For the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing less than excellence, this offering represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly pristine machine.",
